text: This is the closest thing I can think of to what you're asking: <http://vukolic.com/iNetSec_2015.pdf> (Fig. 1)
Folks, we are planning two sessions for the Arch-WG meetings during the F2F.

1. Documentation working session, where we hope to complete the skeleton/outline and starter draft of the consensus layer, business-logic layer functional descriptions and interface document. If you are interested please indicate your availability in this doodle pool: <http://doodle.com/poll/dgfrpexnkqtetxsx>
